{
  "name": "farmduino-desktop",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A desktop app that helps greenhouse owners monitor and control their growing environment even when they are not on-site. With this app, users can easily monitor the temperature, humidity, light intensity, and soil moisture levels in their greenhouse in real-time. They can also receive alerts when any of these levels fall outside of acceptable ranges, and remotely control devices like fans, heaters, lights and water pumps.",
